text: Jesper Eriksson (born August 14, 1996) is a Swedish professional ice hockey goaltender. He is currently playing with Skellefteå AIK in the Swedish Hockey League (SHL) Eriksson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Skellefteå AIK during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Skellefteå AIK players Category:Swedish ice hockey goaltenders
